pis.description:
-	ভিন্ন ভিন্ন পরিস্থিতিতে যোগাযোগের অনুশীলন করা।

-	বয়স, মর্যাদা ও সম্পর্ক অনুযায়ী বাক্যে সর্বনাম এবং ক্রিয়াশব্দ প্রয়োগ করা।
-	ভাষিক ও অভাষিক যোগাযোগের উদাহরণ অনুসন্ধান।
-	পড়ে কী বুঝলাম
-	যোগাযোগে প্রাসঙ্গিক ও অপ্রাসঙ্গিক কথা খুঁজে বের করা।
-	প্রাসঙ্গিকতা বজায় রেখে যোগাযোগের অনুশীলনী করা।

pis.description:
Activity 1.11

The teacher observes the learner’s appropriate use of greetings (Hi/Hello), addressing (Dear/Sir/madam/by name), refusal (polite refusal), and closing remarks (thank you, bye, take care) in the interactions.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students interact with different age groups with a restricted range of words and expressions and with low accuracy and fluency.

pi_attribute.description: Students interact with different age groups using relevant words and expressions according to the contexts with moderate accuracy and fluency.

pi_attribute.title_bn: Students interact with different age groups using appropriate words and expressions according to the contexts accurately and fluently.

pis.name_en: Students produce written texts following appropriate features of greetings, body and closing remarks in a formal and informal letter
pis.name_bn: Students produce written texts following appropriate features of greetings, body and closing remarks in a formal and informal letter
pis.description:
Activity: 14.9

(Students will write the invitation letter individually)

The teacher examines the learners’ scripts to see whether the learners can use the features of greetings, body and closing remarks in the formal and informal pieces of letter writing.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students produce formal and informal texts using the features of greetings, body and closing remarks minimally
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students produce formal and informal texts using the features of greetings, body and closing remarks minimally
pi_attribute.description:
Students fail to determine the formal or informal features of greetings, body and closing remarks in letter writing activity (e.g., email or personal letter or formal application). 
Student fail to demonstrate a range of vocabulary and correct sentence structures in thier writing.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students produce formal and informal texts using the features of greetings, body and closing remarks partially
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students produce formal and informal texts using the features of greetings, body and closing remarks partially
pi_attribute.description:
Students determine the formal or informal features of greetings, body and closing remarks in letter writing activity (e.g., email or personal letter or formal application) appropriately. 
But students demonstrate the moderate use of a range of vocabulary and limited correct sentence structures in their writing.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students produce formal and informal texts using the features of greetings, body and closing remarks appropriately
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students produce formal and informal texts using the features of greetings, body and closing remarks appropriately
pi_attribute.description:
Students determine the formal or informal features of greetings, body and closing remarks in letter writing activity (email or personal letter or formal application) appropriately. 
And students demonstrate a good use of a range of vocabulary and correct sentence structures in their writing.

pis.name_en: Students interact using appropriate ways of greetings, addressing, refusal, and closing remarks according to the specific culture and context
pis.name_bn: Students interact using appropriate ways of greetings, addressing, refusal, and closing remarks according to the specific culture and context
pis.description:
Activity 11.6
(Student individually will write the description)

The teacher observes the learner’s appropriate use of greetings (to known and unknown elders, teachers), addressing (to known and unknown elders, teachers), and refusal (polite refusal) in the Bangladeshi and overseas cultures during the interactions.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students interact in accordance with different cultural contexts using ways of greetings, addressing refusal, and closing remarks minimally
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students interact in accordance with different cultural contexts using ways of greetings, addressing refusal, and closing remarks minimally
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate the limited use of greetings (to known and unknown elders, and teachers), addressing (to known and unknown elders, teachers), and refusal (polite refusal) in the Bangladeshi and overseas cultures during the interactions.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students interact in accordance with different cultural context using ways of greetings, addressing, refusal, and closing remarks partially
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students interact in accordance with different cultural context using ways of greetings, addressing, refusal, and closing remarks partially
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate the appropriate use of greetings (to known and unknown elders, and teachers), addressing (to known and unknown elders, teachers), and refusal (polite refusal) for the Bangladeshi culture but demonstrate limited use of greetings (to known and unknown elders, teachers), addressing (to known and unknown elders, teachers), and refusal (polite refusal) for the overseas cultures during the interactions.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students interact in accordance with different cultural contexts using ways of greetings, addressing, refusal, and closing remarks appropriately
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students interact in accordance with different cultural contexts using ways of greetings, addressing, refusal, and closing remarks appropriately
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate the appropriate use of greetings (to known and unknown elders, and teachers), addressing (to known and unknown elders, teachers), and refusal (polite refusal) for both the Bangladeshi and overseas cultures during the interactions.

pis.name_bn: Students analyse different linguistic features in accordance with the purpose of the texts
pis.description:
Activity: 3.4

(All students will do this activity) 
The teacher examines the learners’ scripts (after the peer checking) to see whether the learners can Identify the definite and indefinite articles in their writing.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students identify different linguistic features with support from the teacher and/or peers
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students identify different linguistic features with support from the teacher and/or peers
pi_attribute.description: Students need support to identify the articles in their writing.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students, with some guidance, identify different linguistic features correctly.
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students, with some guidance, identify different linguistic features correctly.
pi_attribute.description:
Students identify the articles in general in their writing correctly.  
But students fail to indentify the definite and indefinite articles separately in their writing.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students, without any guidance, identify different linguistic features correctly.
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students, without any guidance, identify different linguistic features correctly.
pi_attribute.description:
Students, independently, identify the articles in their writing correctly. 
And students, independently,  identify the definite and indefinite articles separately in their writing correctly.

texts.

Students, guided by the teacher and/or peers, use different linguistic features according to the contexts in producing
texts.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students, with limited guidance, use different linguistic features according to the contexts in producing texts.
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students, with limited guidance, use different linguistic features according to the contexts in producing texts.

Students use some of the articles and pronouns in their writing correctly.  
But students fail to use a few of the articles and pronouns  in their writing.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students, without any guidance, use different linguistic features according to the contexts in producing texts.
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students, without any guidance, use different linguistic features according to the contexts in producing texts.

pis.name_bn: Students practice democratic skills in different situations

pi_attribute.title_en: Students practice one of the democratic skills
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students practice one of the democratic skills
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate either one of the skills i.e., listening to others attentively or respecting others’ opinions or responding logically during the classroom discussion.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students practice any two of the democratic skills
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students practice any two of the democratic skills
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate either two of the skills i.e., listening to others attentively and/or respecting others’ opinions and/or responding logically during the classroom discussion.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students practice all the democratic skills
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students practice all the democratic skills
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate their skills of listening to others attentively and respecting others’ opinions and responding logically during the classroom discussion almost fully.

pis.name_en: Students encourage a democratic attitude in different situation
pis.name_bn: Students encourage a democratic attitude in different situation

pi_attribute.title_en: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to any one part of the democratic
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to any one part of the democratic
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to either one part of the democratic practices (i.e., creating scopes for others to talk or encouraging others to listen attentively or encouraging others to respect others’ opinions or respond logically) during the classroom discussion.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to any two parts of the democratic
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to any two parts of the democratic
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to either any two parts of the democratic practices (i.e., creating scopes for others to talk or encouraging others to listen attentively or encouraging others to respect others’ opinions or respond logically) during the classroom discussion.

pi_attribute.title_en: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to all parts of the democratic
pi_attribute.title_bn: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to all parts of the democratic
pi_attribute.description: Students demonstrate their attitude or mindset to encourage their peers to either any three parts or more of the democratic practices (i.e. creating scopes for others to talk or encouraging others to listen attentively or encouraging others to respect others’ opinions or respond logically) during the classroom discussion.

pis.name_en: নিজের কাজ নিজে করা
pis.name_bn: নিজের কাজ নিজে করা
pis.description:
-এই অধ্যায়ের সাথে সংশ্লিষ্ট 
বিভিন্ন কার্যক্রমে অংশগ্রহণ 
- সঠিক তথ্য উপস্থাপন
-শিক্ষার্থীর পাঠ্যবইয়ের পৃষ্ঠা নং ২, ৮, ৯, ১৫, ১৭, ২০, ২১, ২২, ২৪ 
- শিক্ষার্থীর জমা দেওয়া জীবন ও জীবিকা খাতা (শ্রেণির কাজ ও বাড়ির কাজ যে খাতায় করবে)
- শিক্ষার্থীর জমা দেওয়া   পোস্টার/কোলাজ/কার্টুন/চিত্র/ছবি/তালিকা/গল্প
- ভূমিকাভিনয়ের ছবি/ভিডিও
- পাঠ্যপুস্তকে সন্নিবেশিত স্বমূল্যায়ন ছক
- এছাড়াও বিদ্যালয়ে অবস্থানকালীন সময়ে বিভিন্ন ধরনের কাজ, সংশ্লিষ্ট আচরণ ও অভিভাবক সভায় বা অন্যান্য সময়ে অভিভাবকের কাছ থেকে প্রাপ্ত তথ্য।

(উল্লিখিত কার্যক্রম ও অন্যন্য বিষয়গুলো পর্যবেক্ষণ করতে হবে। ওখান থেকে পর্যবেক্ষণ ও পারদর্শিতার মাত্রা পরিমাপক আচরণ মিলিয়ে মূল্যায়ন করবেন।

pis.description:
ক্লাস ৫ম-৭ম

শ্রেণিতে সব্জি রান্নার অনুশীলন পর্যবেক্ষণ করতে হবে। রান্নার অনুশীলনে পরিচ্ছন্নতা ও নিরাপত্তা বজায় রাখা ও পরিমান ঠিক রাখার রেকর্ড সংগ্রহ করতে হবে। 

শিক্ষার্থীরা নিজেদের বাড়িতে  সব্জি  রান্না করে কিনা; কদাচিৎ করে নাকি মাঝে মাঝে করে নাকি নিয়মিত করে এই সংক্রান্ত  খোঁজ খবর নিতে হবে, সম্ভব হলে ছবি দেখা যেতে পারে।
তাছাড়া সামষ্টিক  মূল্যায়নের সময় শিক্ষার্থীদের তৎপরতা দেখেও এই বিষয়ে তাদের অনুশীলনের মাত্রা পর্যবেক্ষন করা সম্ভব।
